## ▶️ How to Run

1. Clone the repository:

git clone <your-repo-link>
cd <folder-name>


2. Install dependencies:

pip install -r requirements.txt


3. Run the app:

streamlit run app.py


---

## 🌐 Deployment
You can deploy this app using Streamlit Community Cloud.

